<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef7806c7-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2232"><num value="2232">§ 2232.</num><heading> Stenographic reporting service</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Department of Agriculture is authorized to contract for stenographic reporting services.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef7806c8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1944-09-21/ch412">Sept. 21, 1944, ch. 412</ref>, title VII, § 705(b), <ref href="/us/stat/58/742">58 Stat. 742</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
